Could all benefit from the AD Caster category. Im sure there's more, but these are just a few. 

When ER first came out, I actually used it on Warwick in the jungle as a 3rd or 4th item, regardless if it fit or not, and honestly... I was impressed with the outcome. Even by mid - late game, there were skirmishes that left me having to back, or steal the enemy's blue buff cause I ran out of mana. The AA mana sustain from ER helped me a lot, as well as stacking the Lifesteal, and using the CDR to my advantage.
